snippet.title: PROJECT NET | Technical Test Preview Video
snippet.description:
The flames of war rages across higher-dimensional battlefields, and the fabric of the world lines is on the verge of collapse. With annihilation drawing near, the goddess Lunasia turns to Griffin's finest tactical Dolls to assemble a team capable of facing the ultimate crisis.

Project NET is a 3D TPS game officially developed by the Hecate Team, Sunborn Network, which based on the Girls' Frontline Series worldview. Today we bring you a short preview video of the technical testing of our latest piece.

All content in the Technical Test Preview Video does not represent the final quality of the game. We will continue to enrich and improve the game.
